create a individual env file for each services and add these

delivery service
MONGO_URI_DELIVERY_SERVICE=mongodb+srv://gayashaan:8tZESo88njtjrkSq@mernapp.tlvr6cg.mongodb.net/delivery-service?retryWrites=true&w=majority&appName=MERNapp
DELIVERY_PORT=3003
DELIVERY_SERVICE_URL=http://localhost:3003

